{"id": "1523023915000139951", "channel_id": "1523023915000139951", "author_id": "322944911412297728", "author_name": "nowave2863", "content": "Currently, I'm in the top 7% of p-dive scores, which means I get 2/5s the reward of top rank. The rank tiering of p-dive is far too strict and the reward drop-off is too extreme. In Traphase a top 7% score would give you 4/5s the reward of top rank, which seems more reasonable (though I think purple soulforge shards rewards shouldn't be tiered in any game mode). As it stands a player needs to clear madness to get even half of the season rewards.", "timestamp": "2026-07-04T17:53:17.752000+00:00", "thread_id": "1523023915000139951", "attachments": [{"id": "1523023915268706315", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-07-04_135150.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 663411, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1523023915000139951/1523023915268706315/Screenshot_2026-07-04_135150.png?ex=6a4a9a0d&is=6a49488d&hm=5a07ddf42b4f7a66baf544f33ba306df9d0958a871ea669a7a1c67b14e36f90e&"}, {"id": "1523023915612373002", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-07-04_135037.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 741289, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1523023915000139951/1523023915612373002/Screenshot_2026-07-04_135037.png?ex=6a4a9a0d&is=6a49488d&hm=4940b94139793d95af6eb26962d1ec395ba53ed0a6ebce05f06da4dcd84e7162&"}, {"id": "1523023916010967061", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-07-04_134936.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 910182, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1523023915000139951/1523023916010967061/Screenshot_2026-07-04_134936.png?ex=6a4a9a0d&is=6a49488d&hm=b4244b7c50607e71b31ebc078af25f10050410d099561bb9e5208e1a7298bbff&"}]}
